#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.73"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.73:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.73:0.2"
msgid "8. Yamakavagga"
msgstr "8. Pairs"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 73. Paṭhamamaraṇassatisutta → paṭhamamaraṇasatisuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.73:0.3"
msgid "73. Paṭhamamaraṇassatisutta"
msgstr "73. Mindfulness of Death (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.317"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: nātike → nādike (bj, s1-3) | nāṭike (pts1)
msgctxt "an8.73:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā nātike viharati giñjakāvasathe."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Nādika in the brick house."

msgctxt "an8.73:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "an8.73:1.3"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti."
msgstr "“Mendicants!”"

msgctxt "an8.73:1.4"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "an8.73:1.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

msgctxt "an8.73:1.6"
msgid ""
"“maraṇassati, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā "
"amatogadhā amatapariyosānā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when mindfulness of death is developed and cultivated it’s very "
"fruitful and beneficial. It culminates in the deathless and ends with the "
"deathless."

#. VAR: maraṇassatin”ti → maraṇasatinti (bj)
msgctxt "an8.73:1.7"
msgid "Bhāvetha no tumhe, bhikkhave, maraṇassatin”ti."
msgstr "But do you develop mindfulness of death?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.73:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, aññataro bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, one of the mendicants said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an8.73:2.2"
msgid "“ahaṃ kho, bhante, bhāvemi maraṇassatin”ti."
msgstr "“Sir, I develop mindfulness of death.”"

msgctxt "an8.73:2.3"
msgid "“Yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, bhikkhu, bhāvesi maraṇassatin”ti?"
msgstr "“But mendicant, how do you develop it?”"

msgctxt "an8.73:2.4"
msgid "“Idha mayhaṃ, bhante, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "“In this case, sir, I think:"

#. VAR: bahu → bahuṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an8.73:2.5"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ rattindivaṃ jīveyyaṃ, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu "
"vata me kataṃ assā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, if I’d only live for another day and night, I’d focus on the Buddha’s "
"instructions and I could really achieve a lot.’"

msgctxt "an8.73:2.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhāvemi maraṇassatin”ti. (1)"
msgstr "That’s how I develop mindfulness of death.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.73:3.1"
msgid "Aññataropi kho bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Another mendicant said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an8.73:3.2"
msgid "“ahampi kho, bhante, bhāvemi maraṇassatin”ti."
msgstr "“Sir, I too develop mindfulness of death.”"

