msgstr "“But mendicant, how do you develop it?”"

msgctxt "an8.73:3.4"
msgid "“Idha mayhaṃ, bhante, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "“In this case, sir, I think:"

msgctxt "an8.73:3.5"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ divasaṃ jīveyyaṃ, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata "
"me kataṃ assā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, if I’d only live for another day, I’d focus on the Buddha’s "
"instructions and I could really achieve a lot.’"

msgctxt "an8.73:3.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhāvemi maraṇassatin”ti. (2)"
msgstr "That’s how I develop mindfulness of death.”"

