msgctxt "an8.73:9.1"
msgid "Aññataropi kho bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Another mendicant said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an8.73:9.2"
msgid "“ahampi kho, bhante, bhāvemi maraṇassatin”ti."
msgstr "“Sir, I too develop mindfulness of death.”"

msgctxt "an8.73:9.3"
msgid "“Yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, bhikkhu, bhāvesi maraṇassatin”ti?"
msgstr "“But mendicant, how do you develop it?”"

msgctxt "an8.73:9.4"
msgid "“Idha mayhaṃ, bhante, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "“In this case, sir, I think:"

msgctxt "an8.73:9.5"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ tadantaraṃ jīveyyaṃ yadantaraṃ assasitvā vā passasāmi, "
"passasitvā vā assasāmi, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata me "
"kataṃ assā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, if I’d only live as long as it takes to breathe out after breathing in, "
"or to breathe in after breathing out, I’d focus on the Buddha’s instructions "
"and I could really achieve a lot.’"

msgctxt "an8.73:9.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhāvemi maraṇassatin”ti. (8)"
msgstr "That’s how I develop mindfulness of death.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.319"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an8.73:10.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhagavā te bhikkhū etadavoca:"
msgstr "When this was said, the Buddha said to those mendicants:"

#. VAR: yvāyaṃ → yo cāyaṃ (si)
msgctxt "an8.73:10.2"
msgid "“yvāyaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ maraṇassatiṃ bhāveti:"
msgstr "“The mendicants who develop mindfulness of death by wishing"

msgctxt "an8.73:10.3"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ rattindivaṃ jīveyyaṃ, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu "
"vata me kataṃ assā’ti."
msgstr "to live for a day and night …"

#. VAR: cāyaṃ → yo pāyaṃ (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an8.73:10.4"
msgid "Yo cāyaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ maraṇassatiṃ bhāveti:"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: yo pāyaṃ (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an8.73:10.5"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ divasaṃ jīveyyaṃ, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata "
"me kataṃ assā’ti;"
msgstr "or to live for a day …"

msgctxt "an8.73:10.6"
msgid "yo cāyaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ maraṇassatiṃ bhāveti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.73:10.7"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ upaḍḍhadivasaṃ jīveyyaṃ, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, "
"bahu vata me kataṃ assā’ti."
msgstr "or to live for half a day …"

#. VAR: cāyaṃ → yo pāyaṃ (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an8.73:10.8"
msgid "Yo cāyaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ maraṇassatiṃ bhāveti:"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: yo pāyaṃ (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an8.73:10.9"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ tadantaraṃ jīveyyaṃ yadantaraṃ ekapiṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjāmi, "
"bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata me kataṃ assā’ti;"
msgstr "or to live as long as it takes to eat a meal of alms-food …"

msgctxt "an8.73:10.10"
msgid "yo cāyaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ maraṇassatiṃ bhāveti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.73:10.11"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ tadantaraṃ jīveyyaṃ yadantaraṃ upaḍḍhapiṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjāmi, "
"bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata me kataṃ assā’ti."
msgstr "or to live as long as it takes to eat half a meal of alms-food …"

#. VAR: cāyaṃ → yo pāyaṃ (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an8.73:10.12"
msgid "Yo cāyaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ maraṇassatiṃ bhāveti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.73:10.13"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ tadantaraṃ jīveyyaṃ yadantaraṃ cattāro pañca ālope saṅkhāditvā "
"ajjhoharāmi, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata me kataṃ assā’ti—"
msgstr ""
"or to live as long as it takes to chew and swallow four or five mouthfuls …"

msgctxt "an8.73:10.14"
msgid ""
"ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, ‘bhikkhū pamattā viharanti, dandhaṃ maraṇassatiṃ "
"bhāventi āsavānaṃ khayāya’."
msgstr ""
"These are called mendicants who live negligently. They slackly develop "
"mindfulness of death for the ending of defilements."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
#. VAR: khvāyaṃ → yo cāyaṃ (s1-3) | yo ca kho yaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an8.73:11.1"
msgid "Yo ca khvāyaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ maraṇassatiṃ bhāveti:"
msgstr "But the mendicants who develop mindfulness of death by wishing"

msgctxt "an8.73:11.2"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ tadantaraṃ jīveyyaṃ yadantaraṃ ekaṃ ālopaṃ saṅkhāditvā "
"ajjhoharāmi, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata me kataṃ assā’ti."
msgstr "to live as long as it takes to chew and swallow a single mouthful …"

#. VAR: cāyaṃ → yo pāyaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an8.73:11.3"
msgid "Yo cāyaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ maraṇassatiṃ bhāveti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.73:11.4"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ tadantaraṃ jīveyyaṃ yadantaraṃ assasitvā vā passasāmi, "
"passasitvā vā assasāmi, bhagavato sāsanaṃ manasi kareyyaṃ, bahu vata me "
"kataṃ assā’ti—"
msgstr ""
"or to live as long as it takes to breathe out after breathing in, or to "
"breathe in after breathing out …"

msgctxt "an8.73:11.5"
msgid ""
"ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, ‘bhikkhū appamattā viharanti, tikkhaṃ maraṇassatiṃ "
"bhāventi āsavānaṃ khayāya’."
msgstr ""
"These are called mendicants who live diligently. They keenly develop "
"mindfulness of death for the ending of defilements."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an8.73:12.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "an8.73:12.2"
msgid ""
"‘appamattā viharissāma, tikkhaṃ maraṇassatiṃ bhāvayissāma āsavānaṃ "
"khayāyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘We will live diligently. We will keenly develop mindfulness of death for "
"the ending of defilements.’"

msgctxt "an8.73:12.3"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.73:12.4"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
